text: The Feminine Touch is a 1941 American comedy movie directed by W.S. Van Dyke and starring Rosalind Russell, Don Ameche, Kay Francis, Donald Meek, Van Heflin. It was distributed by Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer. ==Other websites== * Category:1941 comedy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Movies directed by W. S.
